# Mods
- Normal
- Insert
- Visual


# Movements
- Left  : h
- Right : l
- Up    : k
- Down  : j

- TOP   : H
- MIDDLE: M
- BOTTOM: L

- Go to n line : n+
- Go to last line : G
- Add new line below : o

# words
- Go to next first word letter  : w
- Go to end current word        : e
- Go to previous word/ specials : b
- Got to previous word not spe' : B


# Save & exit
- Save and exit     : :x
- Save and exit     : :wq
- Exit without save : :q!

# Edit
- INSERTION      : i
- Insert Texte en fin de ligne 	 : A
- Exit Insertion : ESC 
- Delete current letter         : x

# Copy Paste
- Cut 1 line 		: dd
- Cut 2 line 		: 2dd
- Cut current word	: dw

- Copy  line		: yy
- Copy 2line 		: 2yy
- Cipy current word	: yw

- Paste 		: p

# Change:
- Change inside Parens : c i )
- Change inside quotes : c i "

# Delete:
- Delete inside parens : d i )
- Delete inside quotes : d i "
- Delete line : d

# NerdTree
- Switch Tabs : Ctrl + ww
- Open file : o
- Open tabs split H : i
- Open new tabs but leave cursor on tree : go
- Same as i but leave cursor on tree : gi
- Open split v tabs : s
- Same as s but leave cursor on tree : gs
- Close current nodes parents : x
- Goto Root dir : P
- Goto dir : p

